erks can easily reach $40,000-$120,000 annually depending on utilization patterns. DETAILED PILOT BENEFITS TABLE BENEFIT CATEGORY\tSPECIFIC PERK\tSCOPE\tELIGIBLE USERS\tHOW IT WORKS\tEXPECTED OUTPUT/VALUE\tOFFICIAL RESOURCE URL\tMONETIZATION VALUE\tBUSINESS RATIONALE FOR DELTA TRAVEL - DOMESTIC\tUnlimited Standby Travel (Self)\tAll Delta domestic flights\tPilot, First Officer, Captain\tFly for free on standby with S2/S3 priority (higher than regular employees)\t25-50 free domestic flights/year based on schedule flexibility. Value: $2,500-$8,000 annually\thttps://www.delta.com/us/en/careers/benefits\t$2,500-$8,000\tTalent retention; reduces employee churn among senior pilots (10-15 year retention critical) TRAVEL - DOMESTIC\tFamily Standby Domestic Travel\tSpouse/domestic partner and children under 24\tImmediate family members\tS3 priority standby on all domestic flights; eligible family designated with pilot\t15-30 family flights annually. Value: $1,500-$4,800\thttps://www.delta.com/us/en/careers/benefits\t$1,500-$4,800\tImproves work-life balance satisfaction scores; directly impacts retention of pilots with families TRAVEL - DOMESTIC\tParents Standby Travel\tParents of pilot (must be authorized)\tPilot's parents only\tParent(s) registered as pass riders; pilot must book and manage bookings; S3 priority\t6-12 annual parent flights. Value: $600-$1,800\thttps://www.delta.com/us/en/careers/benefits\t$600-$1,800\tCreates multi-generational brand loyalty and extends customer base to parents' networks TRAVEL - INTERNATIONAL\tUnlimited International Standby\tSame-day boarding pass on international routes\tPilot + eligible family (spouse, children, parents)\tAccess to all Delta international flights with SkyTeam partner airlines; S2/S3 priority standby\t3-8 international trips annually (spouse + 1-2 children). Value: $4,000-$12,000\thttps://www.delta.com/us/en/skymiles/medallion-program/international-partner-skyteam-benefits\t$4,000-$12,000\tCompetitive advantage vs. Unite