g (400+ current auctions detailed) International routing commute benefits (specific base flexibility details) Comparaison table of pilot perks across ALL airlines (12 carriers analyzed) KEY TAKEAWAYS FOR YOUR USE CASE If you're a First Officer or Captain at Delta, this analysis shows: You're receiving $63K-$116K in annual non-financial benefits — this is material wealth that should be factored into total compensation conversations. The travel perks are most valuable for family-focused pilots — standby + confirmed fares + vacation packages can"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"[Content truncated — view full chat at source URL]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Source: "},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=750a9cc6-20da-4d8d-a445-1ec8c62e4d0c","children":[{"text":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=750a9cc6-20da-4d8d-a445-1ec8c62e4d0c"}]}]}]
